<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Slid" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">'Slid,</orth> a mean oath, used by such persons as Mr. Slender and Sir Andrew, corrupted from <cit><quote>God's lid:</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 4, 24</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.427" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 427</bibl>. cf. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.228" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 228</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>